scriticism","box":[[547,1286],[1118,1286],[1118,1308],[547,1308]]},{"text":"n(pipan).","box":[[1104,1286],[1307,1282],[1307,1309],[1105,1313]]},{"text":"Third","box":[[1307,1284],[1395,1284],[1395,1307],[1307,1307]]},{"text":"is a transfer to another job in a different factory or to manual labor in","box":[[85,1315],[1377,1316],[1377,1347],[85,1346]]},{"text":"the same factory, while retaining one's","box":[[89,1352],[781,1353],[781,1380],[89,1379]]},{"text":"s wages (often this will occur for a worker","box":[[766,1354],[1518,1352],[1518,1379],[766,1381]]},{"text":"criticizing a leader in an unauthorized wallposter).","box":[[88,1388],[1008,1390],[1008,1417],[87,1415]]},{"text":"Fourth, they will either","box":[[1038,1391],[1466,1389],[1466,1415],[1038,1417]]},{"text":"demote, lower the wages, or change the work assignment of someone, or any","box":[[87,1422],[1378,1426],[1378,1456],[86,1452]]},{"text":"combination of the above measures.","box":[[89,1458],[688,1461],[688,1488],[88,1485]]},{"text":"Theycan alsoextend the amount of","box":[[723,1461],[1325,1459],[1325,1486],[723,1488]]},{"text":"time before","box":[[91,1493],[286,1496],[286,1521],[90,1518]]},{"text":"zhuanzheng, or extend apprenticeship period.","box":[[297,1497],[1116,1497],[1116,1524],[297,1524]]},{"text":"Fifthisto be under","box":[[1107,1497],[1464,1497],[1464,1520],[1107,1520]]},{"text":"supervision","box":[[87,1532],[288,1529],[288,1556],[88,1559]]},{"text":"nwhileremaining","box":[[275,1533],[570,1533],[570,1556],[275,1556]]},{"text":"in the plant (liudui","box":[[557,1532],[940,1532],[940,1559],[557,1559]]},{"text":"i chakan) ,or being under","box":[[927,1533],[1342,1533],[1342,1557],[927,1557]]},{"text":"supervision while remaining","box":[[88,1567],[566,1565],[566,1593],[89,1595]]},{"text":"in the party","box":[[579,1567],[796,1571],[796,1595],[578,1591]]},{"text":"(liudang chakan).","box":[[790,1568],[1127,1567],[1127,1594],[790,1595]]},{"text":"This is for","box":[[1149,1568],[1345,1568],